text: Took a walk from Lavender MRT station to our hotel.
Difficult to access from Little India / Rochor as there is a stroad cutting off connection from the Rochor Canal, and must cross at signalled light a block down
Idyllic plc for jogs, walks, makan, sight see, good view of Rochor River n bridge, plentiful carparks n makan area- North bridge hawker n wet market, near Vic oldies club!
A great place to watch the sunrise.
